No, no.

36
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:28,040
No, you wouldn't have to cover it all.

37
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,640
I see.

38
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,840
Fine. Thank you,
Federico. Have a good day.

39
