58
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:39,240
- Do you have my watch?
- We want 90,000 euros.

59
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,640
- Tomorrow.
- Ninety thousand euros?

60
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:47,680
